{"56beace93aeaaa14008c91e0": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56be4e1facb8001400a502f9": "the panthers finished the regular season with a 15\u20131 record , and quarterback cam newton was named the nfl most valuable player ( mvp ) . they defeated the arizona cardinals 49\u201315 in the nfc championship game and advanced to their second super bowl appearance since the franchise was founded in 1995 . the broncos finished the regular season with a 12\u20134 record , and denied the new england patriots a chance to defend their title from super bowl xlix by defeating them 20\u201318 in the afc championship game . they joined the patriots , dallas cowboys , and pittsburgh steelers as one of four teams that have made eight appearances in the super bowl . <pad>", "56d9895ddc89441400fdb50e": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56be4db0acb8001400a502f0": "super bowl 50 was an american football game", "56be8e613aeaaa14008c90d1": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bea9923aeaaa14008c91bb": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56beace93aeaaa14008c91df": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56d20362e7d4791d009025ea": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56be4db0acb8001400a502ee": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56be4db0acb8001400a502ed": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bea9923aeaaa14008c91b9": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56beace93aeaaa14008c91e1": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56d600e31c85041400946eae": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56d600e31c85041400946eb1": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bf10f43aeaaa14008c9501": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bf10f43aeaaa14008c94fd": "super bowl 50 was an american football game", "56d20362e7d4791d009025e8": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56d20362e7d4791d009025eb": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bea9923aeaaa14008c91ba": "super bowl 50 was an american football", "56bf10f43aeaaa14008c94f